result.formatted_address: Hong Kong, Fanling和豐街28號囍逸G03A 舖
result.name: 譚仔雲南米線(粉嶺囍逸)

reviews.text:
The food in there is great. However I am only giving three stars as the service in there is very unorganized and the place is way too small to let that much people to have food in.
First of all, there are very little space for you to stand at when you are waiting for a table, you will need to keep moving around to let people pass through. In addition to that the seat is way too close together so if you really want to maintain a good personal space. I really wouldn't recommend you to go there during lunch or supper time as it gets very busy.
And lastly the kitchen will cook the food with someone else's order at the same time. So if you are allergic or don't eat a certain food due to religion. Then I suggest you to tell the waiters as you order. This is because last time when I was there I ordered just noodles with vegetables and beef in it. However as I eat I found out there are some pork and other meat in it. I personally don't mind but if you do then let the waiters know beforehand.

跟其他分店一樣味道 但辣粉好像多了一點 今天吃湖南酸辣湯底 
可能新店 人手忙不過來 吃那麼多間 第一次等超久才來米線
終於有譚仔😍
